Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}{\clip(0,50,1920,55)\pos(960,5)\blur4\bord4\3c&H9475D6&}不思議な日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}{\clip(0,55,1920,60)\pos(960,5)\blur4\bord4\3c&H997ED9&}不思議な日々よ
